00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:13.936
The thinking here is that as ancient humans formed larger, more cooperative groups they selected for friendlier individuals.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:23.000
This may have then led to some of the physical characteristics that distinguish us from our closest evolutionary cousins, like smaller round skulls, and subtler brow ridges.

